---
title: Plant Based Spaghetti Bolognese with Crunchy Garlic Rosemary Crumb
description: We love good Plant Based Bolognese & Rosemary Crumb and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/vivera-veggie-plant-based-bolognese-8a750961-551495ac.jpg
